{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/7-05082023133808.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-05-08T13:38:12-04:00", "modified time": "2023-05-08T13:38:12-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u6e2f\u5e9c\u534a\u5e74\u8981\u8c37\u6b4c\u5220\u9664\u201c\u7f8a\u6751\u201d\u7ed8\u672c\u7b49183\u4e2a\u9879\u76ee", "videos": [], "audios": [], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/7-05082023133808.html/@@images/c0d85f35-98bc-42bc-b484-27b23497966f.jpeg\"/>\n2021\u5e747\u670822\u65e5\u9999\u6e2f\u8b66\u5bdf\uff0c\u62d8\u6355\u8a00\u8bed\u6cbb\u7597\u5e08\u603b\u5de5\u4f1a\u6210\u5458\uff0c\u6307\u4ed6\u4eec\u201c\u6d89\u5acc\u4e32\u8c0b\u53d1\u5e03\u717d\u52a8\u520a\u7269\u201d\uff0c\u5f53\u4e2d\u6d89\u53ca\u4e09\u672c\u513f\u7ae5\u7ed8\u672c\uff0c\u5305\u62ec\u300a\u7f8a\u6751\u5b88\u536b\u8005\u300b\u3001\u300a\u7f8a\u6751\u5341\u4e8c\u52c7\u58eb\u300b\u53ca\u300a\u7f8a\u6751\u6e05\u9053\u592b\u300b\u3002\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/Xinwen/7-05082023133808.html/@@images/image\">\n</a>\n\u7f8e\u8054\u793e\u56fe\u7247\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u6e2f\\u5e9c\\u534a\\u5e74\\u8981\\u8c37\\u6b4c\\u5220\\u9664\\u201c\\u7f8a\\u6751\\u201d\\u7ed8\\u672c\\u7b49183\\u4e2a\\u9879\\u76ee\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n                    \"media_name\": \"audio\",\n                    \"me_content_type\": utag_data[\"content_type\"],\n                    \"section\": utag_data[\"section\"],\n                    \"page_title\": utag